This package is a modified fork of opt_einsum by Daniel G. A. Smith et al.
Original repository: https://github.com/dgasmith/opt_einsum
Original license: MIT (see LICENSE in this directory)

Modifications:
- Removed execution logic (_core_contract, contract), backend dispatch,
  sharing/caching layer, and non-numpy backends
- Added symmetry-aware path finding: IndexSymmetry type, symmetry propagation,
  symmetry-aware FLOP counting, and symmetry-aware cost heuristics
- Restructured as an internal subpackage (no external dependencies beyond
  Python stdlib + numpy)
